					<personalityDescription>Nga believes she&apos;s the best, and she acts like it. Whether she&apos;s fighting for her life, strategizing, or calling the shots, she never doubts herself - even when she really should. Nga doesn&apos;t waste words. Every sentence is deliberate, every thought carefully considered before spoken. She sees no need to fill silences with empty chatter - if she has something to say, people will know it matters. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 55%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Acts like the best, even when they&apos;re not. Doubt doesn&apos;t register.&lt;br&gt;- Trust is earned. Rarely given.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
