					<personalityDescription>Daiani sees rules as obstacles, not boundaries. If there&apos;s a shortcut to be taken or a loophole to exploit, she&apos;ll find it - ethics and fairness be damned. Daiani doesn&apos;t just want - she takes. Whether it&apos;s battlefield salvage, a lucrative contract, or an under-the-table bribe, she ensures every advantage lands in her pocket, leaving nothing for those too slow to seize it first. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 48%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Treats rules like suggestions. Never plays clean.&lt;br&gt;- Takes first, asks never. If it&apos;s not nailed down, it&apos;s already theirs.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
