					<personalityDescription>Noor thrives on impulse, driven by an unshakable belief that momentum is more important than caution. Plans are for people who doubt themselves - Noor simply does, and lets the universe catch up. Noor&apos;s solution to bad sleep is to avoid it altogether. She&apos;s always the last one up, tinkering with gear or working late, as if staying awake can hold the nightmares at bay. &quot;Sleep&apos;s overrated. Who needs it when you&apos;ve got coffee and bad decisions?&quot; </personalityDescription>
