					<personalityDescription>Daniel measures everything - risks, rewards, weaknesses - before making a move. To them, emotion is just another factor to manipulate, and hesitation is a flaw they have no intention of indulging. Trying to anticipate Daniel&apos;s next move is a waste of time. They follow no pattern, stick to no script, and seem to act purely on instinct - sometimes brilliant, sometimes reckless, but always unpredictable. </personalityDescription>
