					<personalityDescription>Monica moves through life with absolute certainty, her presence commanding attention without the need for theatrics. When she speaks, it&apos;s with purpose - direct, confident, and impossible to ignore. Every action she takes is calculated. Monica weaves lies, exploits weaknesses, and orchestrates events from the shadows, ensuring that by the time anyone realizes they&apos;ve been played, she&apos;s already won. </personalityDescription>
