					<personalityDescription>Vinh-Anh never truly relaxes - her mind is always scanning, always assessing. Every situation is a puzzle, every interaction a potential threat, and she refuses to be caught  off guard. Vinh-Anh isn&apos;t just prepared - she&apos;s precise. Every knife, or tool in her kit is honed to perfection. She sharpens her combat blade before every mission, during downtime, and even mid-briefing. Her lance jokes that she&apos;d sharpen a laser if she could. </personalityDescription>
