					<personalityDescription>Good enough is never good enough for Taja. She grind herself to the bone, pushing past exhaustion, knowing that even the slightest lapse in preparation could mean failure - or death. She doesn&apos;t stop, because stopping means weakness. Survival depends on knowing when to listen. Taja watches, absorbs, and learns from everything around her, filtering out noise and focusing only on what will keep her ahead of the game. </personalityDescription>
