					<personalityDescription>Tarja doesn&apos;t just hear people - she listens. Whether it&apos;s a new strategy, a fresh perspective, or a hard truth, she takes in information without letting pride or stubbornness get in the way of growth. Every battle, every skirmish, every contract has a plan. Tarja keeps a running list in her HUD - priority targets, terrain advantages, escape routes. &quot;War is just a series of problems to solve,&quot; she says, adding a mental checkmark as she takes down another enemy. </personalityDescription>
