					<performanceExamScore>52</performanceExamScore>
					<personalityDescription>If it&apos;s crazy, reckless, or just plain stupid, Heide-Maria is probably already doing it. She doesn&apos;t just flirt with danger - she buys it a drink and takes it for a ride, laughing in the face of common sense all the way. Heide-Maria doesn&apos;t get involved unless she has to. Other people&apos;s problems, moral dilemmas, or even the bigger picture don&apos;t concern her - she focuses on what directly affects her and ignores the rest. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 53%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Chases danger for fun. Dares what others dismiss. Laughs off rules.&lt;br&gt;- Does the job. Doesn&apos;t care who signs the check.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
