					<personalityDescription>No matter how many times Doria gets knocked down, they get back up stronger. They take every hit, every loss, every failure, and turn it into fuel to keep moving forward. When others falter, Doria stands firm. They don&apos;t just inspire with words - they lead through action, proving time and again that perseverance, heart, and sheer determination can turn the tide of any battle. </personalityDescription>
