					<personalityDescription>Ryuuko doesn&apos;t coddle - she drives people forward. Her words are sharp, her expectations high, but it&apos;s all to make sure those around her survive. If she&apos;s hard on someone, it&apos;s because she refuses to let them fail. Ryuuko has every mission, training session, and equipment check meticulously scheduled. She even sets reminders for &quot;Check Ammo Reserves&quot; and &quot;Pre-Battle Meditation.&quot; Her lance laughs at her - until they realize she&apos;s never the one caught off-guard when an op gets moved up at the last minute. </personalityDescription>
