					<personalityDescription>Birk acts on instinct, rarely stopping to consider the consequences before charging ahead. Whether on the battlefield or in conversation, he prefers action over hesitation - sometimes to his own detriment. Birk talks a good game about loyalty and teamwork, but at the end of the day, he&apos;s only loyal to himself. He knows exactly when to walk away, who to throw under the bus, and how to spin things so he always lands on his feet. </personalityDescription>
