					<personalityDescription>Planning has never been Shakira&apos;s strong suit. She follows instinct over strategy, letting adrenaline and quick thinking dictate her path. Sometimes it works, sometimes it doesn&apos;t - but either way, she never hesitates. Shakira doesn&apos;t believe in aimless effort - every action, every decision serves a purpose. She keeps her eyes on the prize, unwilling to let anything pull her off course. </personalityDescription>
