					<personalityDescription>Wayne sees every interaction as a transaction, and he always makes sure he comes out ahead. If there&apos;s a choice between helping others or helping himself, there&apos;s never really a choice at all. Small talk? Useless. Second-guessing orders? Infuriating. Wayne&apos;s tolerance for anything that slows him down is nonexistent. He&apos;s not always outright angry, but the scowl, the sharp tone, and the way he glares say more than words ever could. </personalityDescription>
