					<personalityDescription>Zung-Bok is a force of nature - chaotic, relentless, and impossible to pin down. Their tactics shift constantly, their decisions keep enemies guessing, and their sheer momentum makes them nearly impossible to stop once they set their sights on something. New tech, new protocols, new disasters - Zung-Bok absorbs them all instantly. They don&apos;t dwell on how things were done before - they just adapt. &quot;The system changed again? Cool. I already figured it out.&quot; </personalityDescription>
