					<personalityDescription>No matter how many times Ryan gets knocked down, he gets back up stronger. He takes every hit, every loss, every failure, and turns it into fuel to keep moving forward. Ryan keeps his watch synced down to the millisecond. He refuses to move before or after his planned schedule, times reloads perfectly, and somehow always knows when trouble is about to start. &quot;We&apos;ve got ninety seconds before this goes to hell,&quot; he mutters. His lance laughs - until he&apos;s exactly right. </personalityDescription>
