					<personalityDescription>Viktoria&apos;s tone alone is enough to set people on edge. Whether it&apos;s the slow, deliberate way she corrects others or the way she smirks when they struggle, she makes it painfully clear that she thinks she&apos;s leagues ahead of everyone else. &quot;Sleep is for people who don&apos;t have things to worry about.&quot; Viktoria is up before dawn, checking weapons, analyzing enemy movements, running drills in her head. &quot;You should sleep, Viktoria.&quot; &quot;So should you,&quot; she fires back. </personalityDescription>
