					<personalityDescription>If it&apos;s crazy, reckless, or just plain stupid, Attis is probably already doing it. He doesn&apos;t just flirt with danger - he buys it a drink and takes it for a ride, laughing in the face of common sense all the way. Attis plays the long game, outmaneuvering competitors before they even realize there&apos;s a game being played. He makes alliances when they serve his goals, breaks them when they don&apos;t, and never loses sight of the bigger picture - his rise to the top. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 46%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Chases danger for fun. Dares what others dismiss. Laughs off rules.&lt;br&gt;- Strategic, cold, and calculating. Plays the game better than anyone.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
