					<personalityDescription>Eugenia doesn&apos;t believe in brute force when superior strategy will do. She dissects enemy formations, anticipates movements, and executes plans with ruthless efficiency - ensuring that by the time the battle begins, she&apos;s already won. Eugenia doesn&apos;t need ideal circumstances - she excels in the worst ones. Whether it&apos;s repurposing old materials, finding alternatives, or just knowing exactly what to prioritize, she gets it done. &quot;You think we don&apos;t have what we need? We do. You just don&apos;t see it yet.&quot; </personalityDescription>
