					<personalityDescription>When others falter, Mal is the rock they lean on. He doesn&apos;t just stand his ground - he inspires others to do the same, proving that true strength comes from never backing down, no matter how impossible the fight may seem. Mal treats every piece of gear like a lifeline, stockpiling supplies in hidden caches and refusing to part with anything that might prove useful. Even when others go without, he holds tight to what he&apos;s gathered - just in case. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 48%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Anchor under pressure. Stands firm and inspires others to follow.&lt;br&gt;- Has backup caches for backup caches. Won&apos;t crack them open unless dying.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
