					<personalityDescription>Tatsui doesn&apos;t slow down, doesn&apos;t stop, doesn&apos;t rest. Whether in battle, in business, or in pursuit of power, he demands more - more resources, more control, more everything - because anything less feels like losing. Tatsui doesn&apos;t just display his accomplishments - he relives them. Every object on his shelf, every framed relic has a meaning, a memory. Whether people see them as inspiring or self-indulgent, one thing is certain: Tatsui remembers everything he&apos;s done. </personalityDescription>
