					<personalityDescription>Ebru charges headfirst into danger without hesitation, trusting instinct and luck to carry her through. Whether it&apos;s an impossible maneuver or a head-on assault, she never stops to ask if it&apos;s a good idea - only if it&apos;s exciting. Ebru is the guy who sighs loudly when someone asks a dumb question. She rolls her eyes, mutters under her breath, and gets annoyed over small things - but beneath the grumbling, she still gets the job done. </personalityDescription>
