					<personalityDescription>Qudamah sees every situation as a business opportunity. If there&apos;s money to be made, he&apos;s already working the angles, cutting deals, and making sure he walks away with the biggest share - preferably at someone else&apos;s expense. Qudamah doesn&apos;t pressure people - he makes them think they&apos;re making their own choices. His calm demeanor, well-placed words, and ability to read a situation let him guide conversations where he wants them to go, without anyone realizing they&apos;ve been led. </personalityDescription>
