					<personalityDescription>Chip is the kind of person who remembers names, listens to stories, and makes people feel valued. Whether in the heat of battle or in downtime between missions, their ability to connect with others makes them the heart of any crew. Chip&apos;s hesitation isn&apos;t a flaw - it&apos;s the weight of too many failures, too many ghosts whispering in their ear. Every decision echoes the last mistake, and sometimes the fear of being wrong keeps them from acting at all. &quot;I&apos;ve seen what happens when you make the wrong call. Sometimes standing still feels safer.&quot; </personalityDescription>
