					<personalityDescription>Some people seek compromise - Carlomaria seeks conflict. He thrives on tension, turning every conversation into a challenge and every challenge into a personal battle. If there&apos;s a peaceful solution, he&apos;s not interested. Carlomaria is ruled by his desires, chasing pleasure with reckless abandon. He consumes, indulges, and takes what he wants without concern for the consequences, leaving behind a trail of broken promises and burned bridges. </personalityDescription>
