					<personalityDescription>Mariana moves like she&apos;s got an internal reactor running at full burn. Whether it&apos;s work, combat, or downtime, she tackles everything with relentless enthusiasm, always ready for the next challenge. Mariana doesn&apos;t just use standard gestures - she&apos;s got a whole extra layer of silent communication. She signals things that don&apos;t need signals, and half the time, her squad isn&apos;t even sure what she&apos;s trying to say. The weird part? She seems to think everyone should already know. </personalityDescription>
