					<personalityDescription>For Marcia, every challenge is simply an opportunity to prove just how infallible she is. She dismisses advice and warnings with a smirk, trusting that her skills and luck will always carry her through, no matter the risk. Marcia&apos;s presence is electric, her passion infectious. Whether rallying troops, seizing opportunities, or leading the charge, she commands attention and action, making things happen while others are still thinking. </personalityDescription>
