					<personalityDescription>Arzhir has survived things that should have killed them - more than once. No matter how many times they get knocked down, they just keep getting back up, proving that sometimes, sheer refusal to die is a strategy all its own. Empathy is a luxury Arzhir doesn&apos;t afford themself. They operate with cold efficiency, avoiding emotional entanglements and unnecessary attachments. Others may struggle with choices - they simply make them and never look back. </personalityDescription>
