					<personalityDescription>José doesn&apos;t let rules, ethics, or principles get in the way of what he wants. If bending the truth, cutting corners, or making shady deals gives him an edge, he won&apos;t lose a wink of sleep over it. José doesn&apos;t believe in second chances or sentimental attachments. If someone can&apos;t keep up, they&apos;re left behind. He sees emotions as liabilities, and nothing - not guilt, grief, or regret - will slow him down. </personalityDescription>
