					<personalityDescription>Artur knows exactly how to push people to their limits - not for their benefit, but for his own. He pulls strings, applies pressure, and always ensures that the cost of his success is paid by someone else. No matter how ruthless the world gets, Artur refuses to compromise his integrity. He sticks to his word, treats people with genuine respect, and never says something just for the sake of appearances. </personalityDescription>
