					<performanceExamScore>48</performanceExamScore>
					<personalityDescription>Thi puts in the work, no matter how long it takes. Whether it&apos;s maintaining her combat unit, planning battle strategies, or honing her skills, she refuses to cut corners - because in her mind, effort is what separates the competent from the dead. Thi doesn&apos;t laugh because nothing is actually funny anymore. But if she doesn&apos;t make some kind of joke, then all that&apos;s left is the weight of everything falling apart around her. So instead, she keeps her voice flat, her delivery emotionless, and her humor just dark enough to keep everyone uneasy. </personalityDescription>
