					<personalityDescription>Elsie gives because they know what it&apos;s like to have nothing. They&apos;ll take the hard jobs, give up their share, and put themself in danger for the sake of others - even when it costs them more than they can afford to lose. Elsie never sits still. They shifts their stance, tugs at sleeves, readjusts posture - always moving, always slightly off-balance, like nothing ever feels fully settled. &quot;I&apos;m fine. Just... this shirt&apos;s wrong. Or maybe it&apos;s just me.&quot; </personalityDescription>
