					<personalityDescription>Isobel never met a fight she didn&apos;t think she could win. Whether it&apos;s in combat, making bets, or mouthing off to the wrong people, Isobel jumps in without thinking - because, really, what&apos;s the worst that could happen? Isobel says what she means and means what she says. She doesn&apos;t believe in playing games or sugarcoating the truth - her words and actions come from a place of honesty, making her a rare presence in a world full of deception. </personalityDescription>
