					<personalityDescription>Money isn&apos;t just a goal for Ti-ann - it&apos;s a skill. She spots opportunities others miss, investing in the right places at the right time, always ensuring that whatever she puts in, she gets twice as much back. Ti-ann has watched people die because someone took too long explaining something. She&apos;s learned that fewer words, faster action means better odds of survival. If she doesn&apos;t need to say it, she doesn&apos;t. </personalityDescription>
