					<personalityDescription>Some warriors fight to survive. Yu-Pei fights for the fun of watching others squirm. Whether it&apos;s taunting an outmatched opponent or deliberately crippling a &apos;Mek just to prolong the suffering, they always make sure to enjoy themself. Yu-Pei always seems to be at the right place at the right time, making the right deals. They know when to buy, when to sell, and when to walk away with a fortune while everyone else is still figuring out what just happened. </personalityDescription>
