					<personalityDescription>There&apos;s no room for hesitation in Addergoole&apos;s world. He steps forward without looking back, his decisions made with the kind of conviction that leaves little space for argument. Whether he&apos;s right or wrong, he never lingers in uncertainty. People are just pieces on a board to Addergoole. He lies, twists the truth, and pulls strings from the shadows, bending others to his will without them ever knowing. If someone thinks they&apos;re in control, it&apos;s only because Addergoole wants them to think that. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 51%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Decides quickly and moves on. Doesn&apos;t second-guess, right or wrong.&lt;br&gt;- Lies, twists, and pulls strings unseen. Lets others believe they&apos;re in charge.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
