					<personalityDescription>Some people call it grit, others call it madness, but Kamil doesn&apos;t care what they think. No matter how much the world tries to grind them down, they keep going, long after anyone else would have quit. Kamil doesn&apos;t waste time on second chances or sentiment. They do what needs to be done, no matter the cost, because in their world, only the strong deserve to survive. </personalityDescription>
