					<personalityDescription>George never hides behind false pretenses or empty words. He stands by his beliefs, never bending to fit expectations, and makes no apologies for who he is - whether people like it or not. George&apos;s been on channels that have gone quiet. Too quiet. The kind of quiet that means something&apos;s gone very wrong. So he keeps his voice loud, his comms open, his presence unignorable. Because if the signal ever drops, if the voices ever cut out, he knows exactly what that means. </personalityDescription>
