					<personalityDescription>Bobby walks into every fight like he owns the battlefield, radiating confidence and daring anyone to prove him wrong. Whether it&apos;s leading the charge or taunting an enemy over open comms, he thrives on being the center of attention - and usually has the skills to back it up. Bobby doesn&apos;t just like to lead - he needs to. Every decision, every plan, every battle has to go his way, and he expects absolute obedience. Anything less is just another problem to be dealt with. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 49%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Owns every fight. Loud, showy, competent. Uses confidence as a weapon.&lt;br&gt;- Must be in charge. Demands obedience - anything else is interference.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
