					<performanceExamScore>49</performanceExamScore>
					<personalityDescription>Risk isn&apos;t something Ema avoids - it&apos;s something she seeks. Whether facing an impossible mission or an untested idea, She meets every challenge with steady resolve and an eager grin. Enough is never enough for Ema. She overcommits, overkills, and overcompensates, whether it&apos;s unloading an entire magazine into a crippled enemy or turning a simple job into an all-consuming mission. If restraint is a virtue, Ema never learned it. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 54%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Seeks out risk. Smiles at impossible odds, eager for the test.&lt;br&gt;- Overcommits, overkills, overdoes. Restraint is a foreign concept.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
