					<personalityDescription>Jane doesn&apos;t go down easy. Even when the odds are stacked against her, she grits her teeth, digs in, and keeps pushing forward. She&apos;s the kind of fighter who walks out of a wrecked &apos;Mek, bleeding but grinning, ready for round two. Jane doesn&apos;t believe in minimalist solutions. If something needs fixing, she reinforces it beyond reason. If something needs supplies, she orders triple the requirement. &quot;Redundancy? No. This is just common sense.&quot; </personalityDescription>
