					<personalityDescription>Doubt is a disease, and Dae refuses to be infected. He knows he&apos;s the best, fights like it, and never flinches - because the moment he does, the enemy will pounce. Confidence isn&apos;t a choice; it&apos;s survival. No sugarcoating, no empty promises - Dae tells it like it is, whether people want to hear it or not. He refuses to play politics or pretend to be something he isn&apos;t, even if it makes him enemies. </personalityDescription>
