					<personalityDescription>Danial doesn&apos;t measure risk the way others do. Where they see danger, he sees duty; where others hesitate, he moves forward. Not because he doesn&apos;t feel fear, but because he refuses to let it define him. Danial has no patience for nonsense. He cuts through distractions and emotions, keeping his mind locked onto the mission. While others get lost in doubt or debate, he moves forward with ruthless efficiency. </personalityDescription>
