					<personalityDescription>Bojana walks into every fight like they own the battlefield, radiating confidence and daring anyone to prove them wrong. Whether it&apos;s leading the charge or taunting an enemy over open comms, they thrive on being the center of attention - and usually has the skills to back it up. Bojana has a way of making everyone feel welcome. Whether it&apos;s a rookie looking for guidance or an old rival at a bar, their easygoing nature and open demeanor put people at ease, breaking down walls before they&apos;re even built. </personalityDescription>
