					<personalityDescription>When Sharadini sets her sights on something, she doesn&apos;t stop until its her. No obstacle is too great, no challenge too daunting - her relentless pursuit of her objectives defines everything she does. Sharadini operates on impulse, changing direction at a moment&apos;s notice. One day, she&apos;s playing it safe; the next, she&apos;s charging into a situation no sane person would touch. Keeping up with her is a challenge - predicting her is impossible. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 52%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Locked in once committed. Obstacles don&apos;t deter - just delay.&lt;br&gt;- No warning before a hard turn. Can&apos;t rely on them to stick to plan.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
