					<personalityDescription>Renata doesn&apos;t just dream of greatness - she&apos;s willing to do whatever it takes to achieve it. Compromise, mercy, and hesitation are for those too weak to seize what they want. She&apos;ll fight, scheme, and claw her way to the top, no matter who gets in her way. Renata doesn&apos;t just fight - she makes sure her gear is invisible until it&apos;s too late. From terrain-matching coatings to active concealment tricks, she takes hiding her equipment as seriously as she takes the fight itself. &quot;If they don&apos;t see it coming, they don&apos;t get a chance to react. That&apos;s the whole point.&quot; </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 54%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Ruthless when needed. Mercy optional. Will climb over anyone in the way.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
