					<performanceExamScore>55</performanceExamScore>
					<personalityDescription>Mercy is just another word for weakness in Evin&apos;s mind. They eliminate threats before they become problems and never lets emotions stand in the way of their ambition. Evin isn&apos;t loud about their support, but it&apos;s always there. A nod at the right time, an unspoken gesture of help, or simply being present when it matters - their strength lies in knowing exactly what people need, even when they don&apos;t ask for it. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 51%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Removes threats before they&apos;re even problems.&lt;br&gt;- Knows what you need before you ask. Delivers, quiet and sure.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
