					<performanceExamScore>45</performanceExamScore>
					<personalityDescription>Ju doesn&apos;t get distracted, doesn&apos;t let setbacks slow her down. Every decision, every action is a step toward her goal. While others waver or compromise, she stays locked onto her objective, no matter what it takes to get there. Ju doesn&apos;t slow down, doesn&apos;t stop, doesn&apos;t rest. Whether in battle, in business, or in pursuit of power, she demands more - more resources, more control, more everything - because anything less feels like losing. </personalityDescription>
					<personalityInterviewNotes>&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Performance Exam:&lt;/b&gt; 55%&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- Laser-focused. Doesn&apos;t waver, doesn&apos;t compromise - just advances.&lt;br&gt;- Operates like the universe owes them more. Never stops collecting.&lt;/html&gt;</personalityInterviewNotes>
